==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unborn
<hw>Un*born"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not born; not yet
brought into life; being still to appear; future.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some <qex>unborn</qex> sorrow, ripe in fortune's womb.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>See future sons, and daughters yet <qex>unborn</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unborrowed</ent>⟦br⟧
